{{infobox person/Wikidata | fetchwikidata=ALL|dateformat=mdy}} '''Ivan Pavlovich Neumyvakin''' ({{lang-ru|Иван Павлович Неумывакин}}; June 24<ref>http://www.dilya.ru/new/040608/</ref> or Jule 7 <sup>according to another source</sup><ref>http://www.mk.ru/social/2013/07/04/879414-kosmicheskiy-prishelets-po-imeni-ivan.html // [[Moskovskij Komsomolets]]</ref>, 1928, near [[Bishkek]],<ref name="id41" /> [[Kirghiz Autonomous Socialist Soviet Republic (1926–36)|Kyrgyzstan]]<ref>[https://tat.rus4all.ru/city_msk/20171113/728388020.html] // [[Rossiya Segodnya]]</ref> &ndash; April 22, 2018<ref name="aaa">https://www.5-tv.ru/news/198781/ // [[Petersburg – Channel 5]] (in Russian)</ref>, [[Moscow]]{{source?|date=May 2018}}, Russia<ref>https://www.5-tv.ru/news/199773/ // [[Petersburg – Channel 5]] (in Russian)</ref>) was a Russian physician, [[Doktor nauk|Doctor of Medical Sciences]],<ref name="r-kosmos" /><ref name="Ogoniok">http://epizodsspace.airbase.ru/bibl/ogonek/1984/40/40-zudov.html // ''[[Ogoniok]]'' № 40, 1984, p. 27 (in Russian).</ref><ref name="Tribuna">Неумывакин И. Если хочешь, не болей [Беседы с д-ром мед. наук, лауреатом Гос. премии ЛатвССР И. Неумывакиным] // ''[[Tribuna|Социалистическая индустрия]]''. — 1988. {See Google Book Search}</ref><ref name="uisi" /><ref name="cec" /><ref name="aaa" /><ref name="ras">[http://www.ras.ru/FStorage/Download.aspx?id=e260dc10-df8f-4051-9fb3-39553c69a48c], [http://www.ras.ru/news/shownews.aspx?id=4295bac9-2910-4d8e-bfd0-ea5020443ec7&print=1] // [[Russian Academy of Sciences]] official site (in Russian)</ref><ref name="fano">[https://fano.gov.ru/ru/press-center/card/?id_4=36932] // [[:eo:Federacia servo pri sciencaj organizaĵoj]] (in Russian)</ref><ref name="iga" /><ref name="p">[https://www.znak.com.pl/kartoteka,ksiazka,57468,Woda-utleniona-na-strazy-zdrowia], [https://www.znak.com.pl/kartoteka,ksiazka,75303,Woda-Zdrowie-i-zycie-Fakty-i-mity] // [[Znak (publisher)]] (in Polish)</ref><ref name="Ноосферное" /> Professor,<ref name